             were indicted for <rs id="t18201206-93-off581" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18201206-93-off581" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201206-93-off581" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18201206-93-cd582" type="crimeDate">9th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-93-off581 t18201206-93-cd582"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-93-off583 t18201206-93-cd582"></join>, six handkerchiefs, value 2 l. 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18201206-93-victim946" type="victimName">
                           Rhoda 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t18201206-93-victim946" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
